{"schema": {"fields":[{"type":"integer","name":"index"},{"type":"string","name":"author_association"},{"type":"string","name":"body"},{"type":"datetime","name":"created_at"},{"type":"string","name":"html_url"},{"type":"integer","name":"id"},{"type":"string","name":"issue_url"},{"type":"string","name":"node_id"},{"type":"datetime","name":"updated_at"},{"type":"string","name":"url"},{"type":"string","name":"user"}],"pandas_version":"0.20.0","primaryKey":["index"]}, "data": [{"index":0,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"see if issues #1748 and #1811 help?\n","created_at":"2012-04-27T09:47:02.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1824#issuecomment-5378203","id":5378203,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1824","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDUzNzgyMDM=","updated_at":"2012-04-27T09:47:02.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/5378203","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars2.githubusercontent.com\/u\/314997?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/zz85","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMxNDk5Nw==","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"zz85","type":"User","id":314997,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/orgs"}},{"index":1,"author_association":"NONE","body":"thanks for your quick answer !\n\nanyway theses issues helped me a little on my understanding of the problem but not for the solution. :(\n\njust added \n\n``` javascript\n var uvGenerator = THREE.ExtrudeGeometry.WorldUVGenerator;\n  var solid = new THREE.ExtrudeGeometry(shapes, { amount: 100, bevelEnabled: true, \n                                                  extrudeMaterial: 0,\n                                                  material: 1,\n                                                  uvGenerator: uvGenerator\n                                                });\n```\n\nand \n\n``` javascript\nvar cd = THREE.UVsDebug(solid);\n  document.body.appendChild(cd);\n```\n\nthe 2D debug canvas draw only lines (no faces) ,  i assume it must be wrong ;)\n\nedit on the problem:\nonly cube edges are textured (i see that when zoom is maximum)\n","created_at":"2012-04-27T11:02:23.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1824#issuecomment-5379320","id":5379320,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1824","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDUzNzkzMjA=","updated_at":"2012-04-27T11:02:23.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/5379320","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars1.githubusercontent.com\/u\/347826?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/come","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM0NzgyNg==","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"come","type":"User","id":347826,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/come\/orgs"}},{"index":2,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"erm. try this uv generator. try disabling the bevel option too (less chance for bugs).\n\n_warning, untested code, try at your risk_\n\n``` javascript\nBoundingUVGenerator = {\n    generateTopUV: function( geometry, extrudedShape, extrudeOptions, indexA, indexB, indexC) {\n        var ax = geometry.vertices[ indexA ].x,\n            ay = geometry.vertices[ indexA ].y,\n\n            bx = geometry.vertices[ indexB ].x,\n            by = geometry.vertices[ indexB ].y,\n\n            cx = geometry.vertices[ indexC ].x,\n            cy = geometry.vertices[ indexC ].y,\n\n            bb = extrudedShape.getBoundingBox(),\n            bbx = bb.maxX - bb.minX,\n            bby = bb.maxY - bb.minY;\n\n        return [\n            new THREE.UV( ( ax - bb.minX ) \/ bbx, 1 - ( ay - bb.minY ) \/ bby ),\n            new THREE.UV( ( bx - bb.minX ) \/ bbx, 1 - ( by - bb.minY ) \/ bby ),\n            new THREE.UV( ( cx - bb.minX ) \/ bbx, 1 - ( cy - bb.minY ) \/ bby )\n        ];\n    },\n\n    generateBottomUV: function( geometry, extrudedShape, extrudeOptions, indexA, indexB, indexC) {\n        return this.generateTopUV( geometry, extrudedShape, extrudeOptions, indexA, indexB, indexC );\n    },\n\n    generateSideWallUV: function( geometry, extrudedShape, wallContour, extrudeOptions,\n                                  indexA, indexB, indexC, indexD, stepIndex, stepsLength,\n                                  contourIndex1, contourIndex2 ) {\n        var ax = geometry.vertices[ indexA ].x,\n            ay = geometry.vertices[ indexA ].y,\n            az = geometry.vertices[ indexA ].z,\n\n            bx = geometry.vertices[ indexB ].x,\n            by = geometry.vertices[ indexB ].y,\n            bz = geometry.vertices[ indexB ].z,\n\n            cx = geometry.vertices[ indexC ].x,\n            cy = geometry.vertices[ indexC ].y,\n            cz = geometry.vertices[ indexC ].z,\n\n            dx = geometry.vertices[ indexD ].x,\n            dy = geometry.vertices[ indexD ].y,\n            dz = geometry.vertices[ indexD ].z;\n\n        var amt = extrudeOptions.amount,\n            bb = extrudedShape.getBoundingBox(),\n            bbx = bb.maxX - bb.minX,\n            bby = bb.maxY - bb.minY;\n\n        if ( Math.abs( ay - by ) < 0.01 ) {\n            return [\n                new THREE.UV( ax \/ bbx, az \/ amt),\n                new THREE.UV( bx \/ bbx, bz \/ amt),\n                new THREE.UV( cx \/ bbx, cz \/ amt),\n                new THREE.UV( dx \/ bbx, dz \/ amt)\n            ];\n        } else {\n            return [\n                new THREE.UV( ay \/ bby, az \/ amt ),\n                new THREE.UV( by \/ bby, bz \/ amt ),\n                new THREE.UV( cy \/ bby, cz \/ amt ),\n                new THREE.UV( dy \/ bby, dz \/ amt )\n            ];\n        }\n    }\n};\n```\n","created_at":"2012-04-27T16:07:06.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1824#issuecomment-5384541","id":5384541,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1824","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDUzODQ1NDE=","updated_at":"2012-05-05T02:27:24.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/5384541","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars2.githubusercontent.com\/u\/314997?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/zz85","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMxNDk5Nw==","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/zz85\/received_events","gra